<Text ObjectRecordID="3797">
	<Original>Важнейший в стратегическом отношении регион был до 43 года ареной ожесточенной борьбы. Для союзников пришло время окончательно выбить германские войска со Средиземного моря и начать освобождение Европейского континета из Италии.</Original>
	<Text>In 1943, after scouring the Germans and the Italian Fascists out of Sicily, the Allies invaded Italy proper, encouraging the Italian Republic to switch sides and opening a semblance of a &apos;&apos;&apos;&apos;second front&apos;&apos;&apos;&apos; against the Germans, but Monty&apos;&apos;s Eighth Army soon found that Churchill&apos;&apos;s dream of a rapid advance up the &apos;&apos;&apos;&apos;soft underbelly of Europe&apos;&apos;&apos;&apos; was in fact a harsh struggle against well-led legions of die-hard Germans who were adept at using Italy&apos;&apos;s difficult terrain to their advantage. Can you strike fear into the hearts of the Wehrmacht defenders with your daring military exploits on the Italian peninsula?</Text>
